1.Write a C program to calculate the sum of the first n natural numbers

#include<stdio.h>
void main()
{
    int n, sum = 0;

    printf("Enter a number : ");
    scanf("%d",&n);

    sum = (n*(n+1))/2;
    printf("Sum of first %d natural number is : %d",n,sum);
}

Output
~~~~~~~

Enter a number : 5
Sum of first 5 natural number is : 15

